_sText:
You've just cleaned your room and you deserve a treat for your efforts, but mommy isn't home so you're left with no choice other than to go get them yourself like the good kid you are. 

surf_tendies was made for the Fall 2020 KSF Mapping Contest and features surf inspired by maps like surf_utopia and surf_pantheon but with a wholesome theme. Although it didn't place in the top 3 the map received much praise for having really fun gameplay for both newer and veteran surfers. 

tier 1
linear
3 bonuses
sv_maxvelocity 5000

Hope you enjoy the map :)
